1.title: Opca zabuna
1.plot: Three generations of the Fazlinovic family live under the same roof: Izet, retired engineer, old communist, and womanizer, Faruk, his son, musician, and Damir, Faruk's son, medical student. Faruk and Izet are worried about Damir's sexuality. At the same time, Faruk's music studio is in financial troubles, because they don't accept to work on any other music, except rock'n'roll. Girl in the video club mixed movie for Damir, with other client's order, causing confusion.

2.title: Crni fond
2.plot: Izet's son Faruk and grandson Damir will do their best to find his ''Black Fond'', a place where he keeps his money.

3.title: Narkomanska posla
3.plot: Izet is trying to quit smoking, but his obsession with cigarettes causes a great confusion in life of Fazlinovic family. Faruk sets up Ivana with his cousin, but thanks to Izet, nothing can be normal in Fazlinovic's apartment.

4.title: Problemi sa stolicom
4.plot: When Izet has digestive problems, Sefika decides to help him with an old recipe. Ivana's pregnancy test causes confusion in Studio Akord and San Remo.

5.title: Stara slika
5.plot: A new neighbor comes to live in an apartment above Fazlinovic. Musician tells Faruk about a high-valued picture owned by Izet.

imdb.plot outline: Three generations (from season four onwards, four generations) of the Fazlinovic family all live in a Sarajevo apartment. The oldest of the family is Izet Fazlinovic. Izet has a son Faruk, who in turn has a son Damir. In season four, Damir's son Dzema is born. The show's title refers to the three main characters, with Izet being Lud (crazy), Faruk being Zbunjen (confused) and Damir being Normalan (normal). The show's plot revolves around humorous situations involving the Fazlinovic clan, their friends and co-workers.
